Package: nlfitr
Type: Package
Title: Fitting models to nonlinear data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: TJ Murphy <medtjm@emory.edu>, Jessica Hoffman<foo@gmail.com, Austin Nuckols<bar@gmail.com>
Maintainer: TJ Murphy <medtjm@emory.edu>
Description: 
    This package simplifies nonlinear regression in R by providing several functions with pre-specified nonlinear model formulas. The fitting input parameter syntax is intuitive. 
    These functions focus on common hyperbolic (dose-response, binding) and exponential (growth, decay) phenomena observed in biological systems. 
    Companion functions include those for simulating responses, with a focus on plot visualizations.
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
